  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Genjutsu (Compulsion)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 22 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 10 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 24</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, E, S</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You create a sound-based illusion that allows you to charm a creature that can hear and understand you clearly, and whose HD does not exceed yours. If a target is being attacked by you or your allies, it receives a +5 bonus to its save. Charmed creatures perceive your words very favorably, and you can make an opposed Charisma check against them to attempt to give them orders, which they will follow unless they are suicidal or obviously harmful to the creature. If you fail an opposed check, you cannot retry it.<br><br>If you or your allies threatens or harms a charmed creature, the effect on them is immediately ended.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 2 Chakra to charm an additional creature within range (up to 1 target per 2 levels total).</p>\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
